name: EPS Series Vol. 5: Believer Dreamer: Junko Mizutani
overview: Mizutani Junko - Believer Dreamer is the fifth disc in the EPS music series made by Antinos Records that features: - CD Player: Play the 2 sides of the single with the songs "Believer Dreamer", "Another time, another place" and the remix of "Believer Dreamer". - Video Editor: Edit the video with the game video editor. - Photo Menu: Browse through three different photo galleries - ESP Original Video: Play the song's video
